it.polimi.se2019.controller.weapon

Class ShootContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.controller.weapon.ShootContext

  • public class ShootContext
extends java.lang.Object
    Parameter boundle passed to every Expression.eval method. Contains contextual information about the current shoot interaction, the game and also a scope with remembered information from the interpreter.
    Author:
    Stefano Montesi
